item.description:
My Perfect Imperfections
[Please read] Hey guys! So here is a tag video that has been requested so many times! Big thanks/shout out to my babes Andreaschoice for creating this fun tag! I had alot of fun! I just filmed it with my macbook because again- its faster to edit and you guys get the jist lol. This tag isn't created to make you depressed. It's not an excuse to step on your confidence. But more of an acceptance that We are not Perfect. Nobody is. Showing you are not ashamed that you are not perfect. Instead- you are embracing your imperfections. The imperfections make you who you are. They are your own trademark. If I spent all my time worrying about my physical appearance- I will Never be happy. There is more to life than looks.
